Classes
----------------------

** Players **
> represent real life indivudals who are playing (alice, bob, charlie)
> have a state of alive/dead
> have an alighment (evil, neutral, etc.)
> have a status (protected)

** Status **

** Role **
> represents a in-game role (e.g. villager, mafia, doctor)


** Game State **
> main control object for game
> keep track of turn number
> cycle day and night phase

